<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_399_r1l11"><expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_399_r1l14"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> freund / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von wegen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_399_r1l15"><expan>Erckıng<ex>er</ex>s</expan> von Saunſheim cʒu Kottenheim / <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_399_r1l16"><expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> brief wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> vnd vvöllen darauf <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_399_r1l17">etwas bedacht ſein ob wir von <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvegen icht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_399_r1l18">gutes darcʒu getun möchten / <expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ı<ex>a</ex></expan> ij̃ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>erhard<ex>i</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_399" id="199r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> freund, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von wegen
                                <expan>Ercking<ex>er</ex>s</expan> von Saunsheim czu Kottenheim,
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        brief wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> und wöllen darauf
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> etwas bedacht sein, ob wir von
                                <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wegen icht gutes darczu getun möchten.
                                <expan>Wan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>i<ex>a</ex></expan> ii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Erhard<ex>i</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
